----------------------------------------------------------------------------
NOTE on dependencies: Taktology references the TopologicPy ontology namespace
(top:), BOT (bot:) and IFC concepts (ifc:) by annotation only (skos:closeMatch,
rdfs:subClassOf). It imports no TopologicPy source code and therefore is not a
derivative work of, nor bound by, TopologicPy's AGPLv3 license. Anyone combining
this vocabulary with TopologicPy *code* must comply with that code's license
separately.
